If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : hotro@homegy.vn

Homegy Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Homegy Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Homegy Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Homegy Smart account in our "Homegy Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Homegy Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Homegy Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Homegy Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Homegy Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Homegy Smart", and you'll be navigated to Homegy login page;
(9). Input your Homegy account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on switch"
“Alexa, turn off switch"
